                from <strong>complex joint replacements and spine disorders</strong> to <strong>fracture care and
                  sports-related injuries</strong>.
              </p>
              <p>
                Dr. Sharma's clinic is built on a single promise — <strong>exhausting every non-surgical treatment
                  option</strong> before considering an operation. Because of this approach, our patients <strong>do not
                  require surgery in 99.9% of cases</strong>.
              </p>

              <p>
                Beyond surgery, Dr. Sharma is a strong advocate of <strong>holistic recovery</strong>, integrating
                <strong>pain management protocols, physiotherapy guidance, and nutritional support</strong> into every
                patient's treatment plan. He has treated patients from across Delhi NCR including , Corporate Patients
                and <strong>diplomatic personnel from several Embassies</strong>.
              </p>

