  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════
     DIET RECOMMENDATION
═══════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="diet-section">
    <div class="diet-grid">

      <div class="diet-content">
        <div class="section-label">Holistic Care</div>
        <h2>Healing Starts on <em>Your Plate & Beyond</em></h2>
        <p>Dr. Sarish Sharma strongly believes that orthopedic recovery is not limited to surgery alone. As part of his
          holistic treatment philosophy, he combines personalized dietary plans — including customized charts for
          vegetarian, vegan, and strict Jain diets — with advanced injection therapies, because what you eat combined
          with targeted treatments directly impacts bone density, joint health, and healing speed.</p>

        <div class="diet-points">
          <div class="diet-point">
            <div class="diet-point-icon">🦴</div>
            <div class="diet-point-text">
              <strong>Bone Strength & Specialized Diets</strong>
              <span>Calcium-rich foods to strengthen bones and prevent fractures, with fully customized dietary plans
                tailored specifically for our vegetarian, vegan, and Jain patients.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="diet-point">
            <div class="diet-point-icon">💊</div>
            <div class="diet-point-text">
              <strong>Vitamin Balance & Deficiencies</strong>
              <span>Addressing critical Vitamin D3 , bone density and B12 (nerve health) deficiencies through
                comprehensive dietary guidance alongside targeted intramascular injections (with no side effects) for
                bone deficiency.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="diet-point">
            <div class="diet-point-icon">💉</div>
            <div class="diet-point-text">
              <strong>Inflammation & Intra-Articular Injections</strong>
              <span>An anti-inflammatory diet combined with non-steroidal injections for pain. We also restore joints
                using viscosupplementation (Hyaluronates/Synvisc), PRP, and Growth Factors.</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="diet-point">
            <div class="diet-point-icon">🩹</div>
            <div class="diet-point-text">
              <strong>Comprehensive Fracture Care</strong>
              <span>Immediate treatment using plaster or aircasts. For delayed and non-union fractures, we utilize
                advanced interventions like intra-fracture bone marrow injections and targeted hip injections.</span>
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="diet-point">
            <div class="diet-point-icon">🚫</div>
            <div class="diet-point-text">
              <strong>Specialized Vegan Care</strong>
              <span>Comprehensive, dairy-free, and meat-free dietary guidance utilizing high-quality plant proteins and
                natural anti-inflammatories to accelerate your orthopedic recovery.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p
          style="font-style:italic;color:var(--teal);font-size:0.88rem;border-left:3px solid var(--gold);padding-left:14px;line-height:1.7;">
          "A balanced diet isn't just good for your heart — it is the foundation of strong bones and pain-free joints. I
          guide every patient on what to eat, alongside advanced targeted treatments, to ensure optimal healing."<br>
          <strong style="font-style:normal;color:var(--navy);">— Dr. Sarish Sharma</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

